quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,Ndifunga ngobusuku xa bugubungela
  92,2,Nangemini xa ivela nokukhanya
  92,3,NangaloWo Wadala isiduna nesikhomokazi
  92,4,Inene imizamo nezenzo zenu zahlukahlukene
  92,5,"Lowo unikelayo (ngamalizo), esoyika uAllâh"
  92,6,Akholelwe kokulungileyo (kuAllâh)
  92,7,Inene Siya kumenzela mpuluswa indlela yokuhamba lula
  92,8,"Ke yena lowo unyolukileyo, uligogotya, ezicingela ukuba akaxhomekekanga ntweni"
  92,9,Aphikisane nokulungileyo
  92,10,Siya kumenzela mpuluswa indlela eya ekungcoleni
  92,11,Kanti buza kumnceda ntoni ubutyebi bakhe xa esiya entshabalalweni
  92,12,Inene kukuThi ukunika isiKhokelo
  92,13,Yaye inene seseThu isiphelo (uBomi oBuzayo) nesiqalo (ubomi beli hlabathi)
  92,14,"Ngoko\tke\tNdinilumkisile\tngoMlilo\todwanguzayo (wesiHogo)"
  92,15,Akukho mntu uza kungena kuwo ngaphandle kosisingcoli (owala ukukholwa kwi-Islam)
  92,16,"Ophikayo, atshikile"
  92,17,"Ke bona abamoyikayo uAllâh, baya kususwa babe kude kuwo (uMlilo)"
  92,18,"Lowo\tuchitha\tubutyebi\tbakhe\tekuzongezeleleni ukuhlambuluka komphefumlo wakhe"
  92,19,Ongenzeli (kunconywa) nakuhlawulwa ngumntu
  92,20,"Ngaphandle\tkokufuna\tukukholisa\tiNkosi\tyakhe Ephakamileyo, (uAllâh)"
  92,21,Kungekudala uya kwaneliseka (xa engeniswa ePaladesi)